{
  "id": "63bd721e18ab06001e12ced9",
  "title": "真理集合",
  "created": 1673359902,
  "updated": 1674476195,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63bd721e18ab06001e12ced9",
      "text": "真理集合",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359902,
      "updated": 1673359902
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c000002477f7",
      "text": "from [論理と集合から始める数学の基礎 読書会]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1673359903
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c000002477f8",
      "text": "[真理集合]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1673359903
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c000002477f9",
      "text": " [$ P(x)]が[自由変数][$ x]の述語で、[$ x]の変域が集合[$ U]であるとき、命題[$ P(x)]が真である[$ U]の要素全体の集合のこと",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1673359903
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c000002477fa",
      "text": "  [$ \\{x|P(x)\\}]で表す",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476092
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7a315e90c00000652481",
      "text": "  仮に[$ A=\\{x|P(x)\\}]となった場合、[$ A]は[$ U]の[部分集合]だといえる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476080,
      "updated": 1674476099
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c000002477fb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7a2d5e90c0000065247f",
      "text": "テキストの例",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476076,
      "updated": 1674476087
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c000002477fc",
      "text": " 例3.3~3.5",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c000002477fd",
      "text": "  3.3は比較的簡単な例[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c000002477fe",
      "text": "   [$ x]の変域を自然数全体の集合[$ \\N]とし、自由変数の述語[$ P(x)]が[$ x<5]を表している",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c000002477ff",
      "text": "   このとき真理集合を[$ A]とすると",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c00000247800",
      "text": "   [$ A=\\{x|x<5\\}]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c00000247801",
      "text": "    [外延的記法]で書くと[$ A=\\{1,2,3,4\\}]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c00000247802",
      "text": "  3.4は[$ x]の変域によって真理集合の様子が全く異なってくることの例",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c00000247803",
      "text": "   上のAでいうと[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c00000247804",
      "text": "    xの変域が自然数全体の集合[$ \\N]なら[$ A=\\{1,2,3,4\\}]となる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c00000247805",
      "text": "    でもこれが実数全体の集合[$ \\R]なら……どうなる？",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c00000247806",
      "text": "     これは外延的記法では書けない、無数にある",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c00000247807",
      "text": "      有理数とその間にあるたっくさんの無理数",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c00000247808",
      "text": "     [$ A=\\{x<5\\}]？",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c00000247809",
      "text": "  3.5は方程式の[解集合]([解空間])",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c0000024780a",
      "text": "   >一般に, [$ x]の変域が[$ U]で, 自由変数[$ x]についての述語[$ P(x)]が[$ x]についての方程式であるとき, [$ P(x)]をみたす[$ U]の要素を, 方程式[$ P(x)]の解といいます. そして, [$ P(x)]の真理集合[$ \\{x|P(x)\\}], すなわち, 方程式[$ P(x)]の解全体の集合を, 方程式[$ P(x)]の解集合または解空間といいます. (p.27)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c0000024780b",
      "text": "   例えば[$ x]の変域が実数全体の集合[$ \\R]で、自由変数[$ x]の述語を「[$ x^2-2x+1=0]」とする[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c0000024780c",
      "text": "    このときの真理集合は[$ \\{x|x^2-2x+1=0\\}]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c0000024780d",
      "text": "     外延的記法であらわすと[$ \\{1\\}]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c0000024780e",
      "text": "     解全体の集合を解集合・解空間と呼ぶので、[$ x^2-2x+1=0]の解集合は[$ \\{1\\}]となる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c0000024780f",
      "text": "  3.6は変域すべてが真理集合となる場合、3.7は変域すべてが真理集合とならない場合",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1674476075
    },
    {
      "id": "63bd721f5e90c00000247810",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1673359903,
      "updated": 1673359903
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7a875e90c00000b4632d",
      "text": " [2つの述語が同値であるとは、真理集合が一致すること](定義)",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476166,
      "updated": 1674476191
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7a875e90c00000b4632e",
      "text": "  たとえば？[cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476166,
      "updated": 1674476195
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7a875e90c00000b4632f",
      "text": "   変数[$ x]の変域を[$ \\N]として、[$ P(x),Q(x)]を自由変数[$ x]の述語であるとしよう",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476166,
      "updated": 1674476166
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7a875e90c00000b46330",
      "text": "   このとき[$ P(x)]が[$ x+1=3]、[$ Q(x)]が[$ x+4=6]だとする",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476166,
      "updated": 1674476166
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7a875e90c00000b46331",
      "text": "    [$ P(x)]の真理集合は[$ \\{2\\}]のみ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476166,
      "updated": 1674476166
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7a875e90c00000b46332",
      "text": "    同じく[$ Q(x)]の真理集合は[$ \\{2\\}]のみ",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476166,
      "updated": 1674476166
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7a875e90c00000b46333",
      "text": "   [$ \\{x|P(x)\\}=\\{x|Q(x)\\}]であるので、両者は同値だといえる",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476166,
      "updated": 1674476166
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7a875e90c00000b46334",
      "text": "    [$ P(x) \\iff Q(x)]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476166,
      "updated": 1674476166
    },
    {
      "id": "63ce7a875e90c00000b46335",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1674476166,
      "updated": 1674476166
    }
  ]
}